#

Truffle-infused Wild Mushroom Risotto

$25
600 kcal
Difficulty: 70%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetarian

Tags:

gourmetItalianvegetarian

Description

A rich and creamy risotto with wild mushrooms, accented by the luxurious aroma of truffle oil.

Ingredients

  • Arborio rice: 1 cup
  • Wild mushrooms (such as porcini, shiitake, and chanterelles): 200 grams
  • Vegetable stock: 4 cups
  • White onion: 1, finely chopped
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • Truffle oil: 1 tablespoon
  • Butter: 2 tablespoons
  • Olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • Dry white wine: 1/2 cup
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Fresh parsley: 2 tablespoons, chopped
